Summary: An object that looked like a plane at first.came toward us as we were sitting around a fire on Maconi Park Beach, North Eastham Cape Cod. The object emitted a weird green light on us that was shimmery and seemed like a bar code.
divs: Sighting Detailsfter it passed us it continued on untill it passed the nexted bonn fire about 300 yards away and then it went out. the party at the other fire immeadiately left the beach. W gathered our things and put out our fire and left shortley there after.The park ranger met uus at the stairs and questioned us all as to what we saw. the next day we called the park rangers office to find out what it was.they had no information except a note saying they were called to check out a spectical. If you know of anything about this please let us know. Thank you,
